Obrigada, Nadia.

377
00:17:10,638 --> 00:17:12,074
E os arquivos do Tan?

378
00:17:12,118 --> 00:17:13,336
Solicitei ontem.

379
00:17:13,380 --> 00:17:14,555
Achei que já
estivesse aqui hoje.

380
00:17:14,598 --> 00:17:16,078
Sim, estão.

381
00:17:16,122 --> 00:17:18,515
Hughes meio que os inteceptou.

382
00:17:18,559 --> 00:17:19,951
